&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Department of Elderly Medicine: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a substantive SAS doctor to work 0.7 PA per week in the Department of Medicine for the Elderly at Poole Hospital commencing 3rd March 2021. Applicants for this post will be supported to pursue a CCT in order to subsequently apply for a consultant post if desired. This post will rotate through all aspects of the department including acute older person’s admissions unit (RACE), downstream wards, ortho-geriatrics and community based services to provide a broad experience of training and cover the Geriatric Medicine curriculum.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
